  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0daf\u0db8\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Lowers fuel prices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Petroleum Statutory Corporation took steps to lower fuel prices today (17) afternoon.",
        "Accordingly, a liter of octane 92 petrol and auto diesel have been reduced by 20 rupees, a liter of octane 95 petrol and a liter of super diesel have been reduced by 10 rupees.",
        "With the price revision, Octane 92 petrol fell by Rs 450, Octane 95 petrol by Rs 540, Auto diesel by Rs 440 and Super diesel by Rs 510.",
        "The Petroleum Corporation also announced that the price reduction will be effective from 10:00 tonight.",
        "A senior official of the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation said that this price drop happened according to the adjustments of the fuel price formula in the last two weeks."
      ],
